window.bookSummaryJSON = "<b><i>A shifter's secret, an agent's mission, and a love that defies the odds in a captivating tropical escape.<br><br>Violet</i></b><br><br>I rose above my past to become a famous pop star, only to have my secret identity as a wolf shifter exposed on social media. Desperate for peace amidst the chaos, I retreat to the idyllic Casa del Lobo, a tropical resort owned by a trusted friend. My path unexpectedly crosses with a captivating masseuse, and our instant connection is impossible to comprehend. In a world where fated mates no longer exist, trusting the bond is a risk that may be too dangerous to take.<br><br><b><i>Jesse</i></b><br><br>As a covert agent for the Bureau of Shifter Affairs, my mission is to uncover the truth behind the disappearances of multiple shifters at Casa del Lobo. Disguised as a masseuse, fate deals me a wild card when I encounter the enigmatic Violet Raine. My instincts roar to life, but with my primary suspect being her friend, the Bureau expects me to exploit her trust. Torn between duty and desire, can I protect both the missing shifters and the woman who's stolen my heart?<br><br>Dive into Trouble in Paradise, an electrifying paranormal romance that will grip you from the first page. Witness Jesse and Violet's struggle to unravel the secrets of Casa del Lobo, navigating a world where fated mates are a distant memory, and humans are suddenly aware of the existence of shifters. Overflowing with suspense, humor, and irresistible chemistry, Trouble in Paradise is an exhilarating adventure that will leave you breathless."; 
